title: (Tues Full) Lunchbox’s Top 10 Cringiest Moments + Can You Spot the Troll by the Instagram Bio? Game + Woman Wakes Up To A ____ In Bed with Her! What was it??
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Lunchbox’s Top 10 Cringiest Moments + Can You Spot the Troll by the Instagram Bio? Game + Woman Wakes Up To A ____ In Bed with Her! What was it??
description:
Bobby finally reveals what has made the Top 10 moments where Lunchbox made us all cringe. We play a game where we have to spot the troll based on their Instagram bio. Bobby shares a story about a woman who was shocked to wake up next to something in her bed. We guess what it was.
